description: This API accepts body content as multipart/form-data and application/octet-stream. When using multipartmultiple image files can be sent at once, with a maximum of 64 files

isbatchsuccessful.description: True if all of the images in the batch were created successfully, otherwise false.

images.description: List of the image creation results.

tag_ids.description: The tags ids with which to tag each image. Limited to 20.
